title: Comfortable Foldable and Portable Laptop Table Stand/Study Table/Bed Table
description:
About Product:-

Ergonomic & Rounded Edges/Non-Slip Legs/Engineered Wood/ColorMULTIPURPOSE LAPTOP LAP DESK: This laptop stand is extremely practical, can be used as a laptop workstation, laptop table for bed, a children's bed table, a mini writing table, a standing table for office work, laptop couch table, or a book/tablet table, picnic table.

  • STURDY AND ANTI SLIP: The foldable sofa breakfast Tray is made of MDF while the legs are made of steel with powder-coated finished, more strong and sturdy, curved ergonomic tabletop designed for sitting. This table will last for a lifetime and will remain corrosion-free. The steel feet are covered with a black sponge for a good anti-slip effect.
  • WHAT YOU GET: 1X Laptop bed stand desk
  • EXTRA SIZE: The size of this laptop desk is:23’’x16’’x0.4’’(58.5x40.8x1.7cm) when it‘s folding, Such a large size is suitable for a 17'' laptop or smaller, also with space for a mouse. Built-in iPad stands groove for holding iPad or kindle.
  • LIGHTWEIGHT AND PORTABLE: This notebook stand is light enough(only5.4lb/2.45KG) and our clever folding design allows the legs to fold flat so you can easily carry it around and use it to work from anywhere. No need to install, open it and use it after you got this product.
